summary: This document is an email forwarding a signed warrant for three devices related to the Epstein case, sent from the court to criminal case operations. It appears to be part of ongoing legal proceedings regarding evidence collection.

events.title: Warrant signing for devices
events.description: A signed warrant for three devices related to the Epstein case was forwarded via email from the court to criminal case operations.

keyFacts: A signed warrant was issued for three devices related to the Epstein case.
The warrant was forwarded via email on October 28, 2020.
The document indicates ongoing legal proceedings involving evidence collection.
The email was sent from the court to criminal case operations.
The subject references 'EPSTEIN; AUSA' indicating involvement of the U.S. Attorney's Office.
